targets.rawSql:
SELECT name from server_user
WHERE server_user.id = 2

SELECT MAX(server_userbill.updatedat)
	FROM server_userbill
	WHERE server_userbill.user_id = 2
SELECT MAX(server_userbill.amount) FROM server_userbill WHERE server_userbill.user_id = 2

SELECT SUM(server_measurement.consumption) as month, date_trunc('month', server_measurement.measuredat) as time
	FROM server_measurement INNER JOIN server_equipment ON server_measurement.equipment_id = server_equipment.id
	WHERE server_measurement.measuredat >= date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) and server_equipment.user_id = 2
	GROUP by time

SELECT SUM(server_measurement.consumption)
	FROM server_measurement INNER JOIN server_equipment ON server_measurement.equipment_id = server_equipment.id
	WHERE server_measurement.measuredat >= date_trunc('year', CURRENT_DATE) and server_equipment.user_id = 2 and extract(month FROM server_measurement.measuredat) = 1

SELECT
  $__unixEpochGroupAlias(id,$__interval),
  count(id) - 1 AS "id"
FROM "server_user"
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT SUM(server_measurement.consumption)
	FROM server_measurement INNER JOIN server_equipment ON server_measurement.equipment_id = server_equipment.id
	WHERE server_measurement.measuredat >= date_trunc('month', CURRENT_DATE)
	AND server_equipment.user_id = 1
	GROUP BY server_equipment.user_id

SELECT SUM(server_measurement.consumption)/COUNT(server_equipment.user_id)
	FROM server_measurement INNER JOIN server_equipment ON server_measurement.equipment_id = server_equipment.id
	WHERE server_measurement.measuredat >= date_trunc('month', CURRENT_DATE)
	AND server_equipment.user_id > 1
